value.title: Right Now, Managing AI Agents is About as Much Work as Managing Humans. Just Different Work.
value.content: Here’s something almost nobody tells you when you deploy your first AI agent: you’re not eliminating management overhead. You’re trading one type of work for another. It’s different work. But it requires about as much time for oversight, review, and training as managing humans did. We’ve deployed 20+ AI agents at SaaStr over the past... Continue Reading
